    <br>
    <p>●<a href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/scriptures/pgp/moses/1?lang=jpn&amp;id=1-11,27-29,37-39#p1">モーセ１章１ー11、27−29、37-39</a><br>
    </p>
